Host *
ForwardX11 yes
ForwardX11Trusted yes
Protocol 2
PermitLocalCommand yes
Compression yes
CompressionLevel 9
ConnectionAttempts 3
NumberOfPasswordPrompts 3
ServerAliveCountMax 3
ServerAliveInterval 10
TCPKeepAlive yes
Cipher aes256-cbc
Ciphers aes256-cbc,aes192-cbc,aes128-cbc,blowfish-cbc,arcfour
ForwardAgent yes
HashKnownHosts yes
ProxyCommand monkeysphere ssh-proxycommand %h %p
VisualHostKey yes

